Task: dialup
Section: hware
Description: Dialup internet
 This task selects packages that address special needs of computers
 using a slow part-time dialup connection (by modem, ISDN, or similar).
Key:
 ppp
 isdnutils
Packages:
 # Modem:
 diald
 pppconfig
 wvdial
 # Other handy stuff for dialup connections:
 fetchmail
 wwwoffle
 leafnode
 lftp
 dnsmasq
 resolvconf
